comments: Washington (CHA) reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball and it is last touched by Beal (WAS) before going out of bounds.  After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of Wizards possession is overturned to Hornets possession.
Batum (CHA) slightly extends his arm into Bryant (WAS) as he sets the pick but the contact is marginal.
Bryant (WAS) is in the lane for three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Bertans (WAS) makes marginal contact to Rozier's (CHA) body and does not affect the driving shot attempt.
Washington (CHA) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Bryant (WAS) after the release that does not affect his shot attempt.
Smith (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position on Rozier (CHA) and the contact is incidental.
McRae (WAS) briefly grasps Batum's (CHA) arm, but does not affect his ability to defend at the start of the drive.
Batum (CHA) makes marginal contact to McRae's (WAS) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Zeller (CHA) makes marginal contact with Beal (WAS) as he sets the screen.
Zeller (CHA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of McRae (WAS) and absorbs the contact.
Williams (CHA) commits a take foul on Beal (WAS).
Smith (WAS) makes marginal contact to Rozier's (CHA) arm that does not affect his control of the ball during the drive.
Rozier (CHA) commits a take foul on McRae (WAS).
